                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10129" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1513</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">273 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新纪元医疗：从“刹车失灵”到“数字导航”的业财融合突围战</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The business-finance integration breakthrough battle of New Era Medical</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄荟婕，谢晓燕，李楠，邓雨婷，夏丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内蒙古工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中山市新纪元医疗科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业财融合；财务变革；平衡计分卡；战略地图</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Business-finance integration; Financial transformation; Balanced Scorecard; Strategy map</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新创企业在高速扩张中普遍面临业财失衡的挑战。本案例详细阐述了新纪元医疗对业财融合的艰难探索和逐步深化过程。从应对财务刹车失灵的数据融合与系统融合，到消除部门壁垒的认知融合和组织融合，再到增强内驱动力的战略融合和绩效融合，新纪元医疗最终实现了财务数字导航的业财价值深度融合。通过对本案例的讨论学习，学生将掌握业财融合的内涵及其内在逻辑，理解BP、低代码、ERP等相关概念，分析业务与财务融合在不同维度的执行策略，并能够运用战略地图、平衡计分卡等管理工具。本案例的学习有助于培养学生运用理论知识和方法工具解决实际业财融合问题的能力，培育学生数据理性与商业洞察相融合的决策素养，同时为新兴企业如何实现业务与财务融合提供了有益的参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Startups commonly face the challenge of business-finance misalignment during rapid expansion. This case details the arduous exploration and progressive deepening of business-finance integration at New Era Medical. From addressing financial &quot;brake failure&quot; through data integration and system integration, to eliminating departmental barriers via cognitive integration and organizational integration, and further enhancing internal drive through strategic integration and performance integration, New Era Medical ultimately achieved value-driven, digitally navigated business-finance synergy. Through case study and discussion, students will grasp the essence and underlying logic of business-finance integration, understand concepts such as Business Partner, low-code platforms, and ERP, analyze implementation strategies across different dimensions of integration, and apply management tools like strategy maps and the Balanced Scorecard. This case cultivates students&#39; ability to solve real-world integration challenges using theoretical knowledge and methodologies, fosters decision-making literacy that integrates data rationality with business acumen, and provides actionable insights for emerging enterprises seeking effective business-finance alignment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业财融合；平衡计分卡；战略地图；低代码；BP；ERP</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
